title: 2000AD 1852 (2013) (Digital) (Nahga-Empire)
description:
Story by Michael Carroll, Ian Edginton, Pat Mills
Art by Paul Davidson, INJ Culbard, James McKay
Colors by Chris Blythe, Gary Caldwell
Letters by Annie Parkhouse, Ellie De Ville, Simon Bowland
Cover by INJ Culbard

Publisher: 2000AD
Release Date: October 2, 2013

This week's 2000 AD is ex-SCYTHE-ing as the robot assassin gets a little too close for comfort in Brass Sun! 2000 AD Prog 1852 is out on Wednesday 2nd October and continuer the fresh new stories ideal for new readers! Available worldwide day-and-date digital through the 2000 AD webshop or the 2000 AD iPad app, it's never been easier to start reading this powerhouse of British comics.
